<h2>Focusing</h2>

	<p>If you would like to work with me to <b>learn focusing</b> as a <b>self-help</b> practice, or you would like to deepen your focusing experience, you are very welcome to contact me to discuss what you need. Focusing can work in person or over video link. </p>

<p>I am also very open to supporting your self-discovery through <b>art and imagery</b> during counselling or focusing sessions.</p>

